        "name": "Yang Sheng",
        "email": "ys@whamcloud.com",
        "username": "ys"
      },
      "date": "2015-12-21 12:52:58.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nHi, Emoly, Looks like '-w' will absence in future rmmod. So it would also failed in new release even with version check. We may trying to found root cause or loop rmmod by ourselves at worst case. So i suggest land this patch first and look what happens.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
